WEBVTT

00:02:59.400 --> 00:03:00.816
That helped me a lot.

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:03.496
It motivated me to change my life

00:03:03.520 --> 00:03:06.120
and take a hard time as a game.

00:03:07.240 --> 00:03:09.936
Now, as an artist,

00:03:09.960 --> 00:03:12.856
I am creating different
lives for my models

00:03:12.880 --> 00:03:18.336
in order to give them the experience
of being someone else in reality.

00:03:18.360 --> 00:03:20.616
Through the photographic process,

00:03:20.640 --> 00:03:24.936
all of my models
become like silent movie actors.

00:03:24.960 --> 00:03:26.856
They are captured at the moment

00:03:26.880 --> 00:03:31.256
when they believe
in being someone else entirely.